ptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.39"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"136:39"],"; )"],["li","they have shed innocent",["i","blood"],", which crieth from the ground:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.36"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"136:36"],";"]]]]],"refs":null}
